    <modellingAndValidation>
      <representativeness systemModelId="290c1f85-4cc4-4fa1-b0c8-2cb7f4276dce">
        <systemModelName xml:lang="en">Allocation, cut-off by classification</systemModelName>
        <samplingProcedure xml:lang="en">Extrapolation from European dataset. Literature data, representativeness estimated for min. 80 % of European (EU + GB, NO, CH) production.

Multi-functionality is solved in accordance with IFEU/PlasticsEurope (2021) with a flow specific approach. Feedstock is partitioned to all allocatable outputs by mass, whereas all the other inputs and outputs (energy and other input, emissions and solid wastes) are assigned only to the reference products (benzene, toluene, o-xylene, p-xylene and xylenes, mixed) based on process information.

References:

IFEU/PlasticsEurope (2021): Eco-profile of Steam Cracker Products: Ethylene, Propylene, Butadiene, Pyrolysis Gasoline, Ethylene Oxide (EO), Ethylene Glycols (MEG, DEG, TEG).</samplingProcedure>
        <extrapolations xml:lang="en">Extrapolation from European dataset. Uncertainty has been adjusted accordingly.</extrapolations>
      </representativeness>
